algebraDomain

Class AlgebraTask

  • java.lang.Object
    • engine.CognitiveTask
      • algebraDomain.AlgebraTask

  • public class AlgebraTask
extends CognitiveTask
    Implementation of a cognitive task for the algebra domain, where the task is to solve simple one-step/two-step equations. The following domain dependent (i.e. algebra) elements must be defined: 1. A string representation of a typical interface that can be used to perform the task (i.e. interfaceLayout). 2. A method to break down the name of the problem into the parts that need to update the working memory for its initial state.
    Author:
    Nikolaos Barmpalios {nbarmpalios@gmail.com}
